    dc:description "Figure 43. Holotype female of Lissonota semistriata Walker, 1874 (= Bassus semistriatus (Walker, 1874)): (a) labels (b) lateral habitus (c) head, lateral view (d) head, anterolateral view (e) head, dorsal view (f) wings (g) metasoma, dorsal view (h) mesosoma, lateral view (i) mesoscutum and scutellum, dorsal view (j) propodeum, dorsal view." ;
